Frontend README
Language Learning Platform – Frontend

This is the frontend of the Language Learning Platform built using React + Vite.

Users can:

Sign up / Login

Learn courses

Take quizzes

Practice flashcards

Track learning streaks

🚀 Tech Stack

React

Vite

React Router

Axios

CSS

📂 Project Structure
frontend
│
├── src
│   ├── components
│   │   ├── Navbar.jsx
│   │   └── ProtectedRoute.jsx
│   │
│   ├── pages
│   │   ├── Home.jsx
│   │   ├── Dashboard.jsx
│   │   ├── Courses.jsx
│   │   ├── Lessons.jsx
│   │   ├── Quiz.jsx
│   │   ├── Flashcards.jsx
│   │   ├── Login.jsx
│   │   └── Signup.jsx
│   │
│   ├── api.js
│   ├── App.jsx
│   ├── main.jsx
│   └── index.css
⚙️ Installation

1️⃣ Go to frontend folder

cd frontend

2️⃣ Install dependencies

npm install
▶️ Run the Project
npm run dev

Runs on:

http://localhost:5173
🌐 Backend API URL

Example:

https://langugae-learning-platform-1.onrender.com

Example request:

GET /courses
GET /quiz/1
GET /api/flashcards/random
GET /streaks/1
📊 Features
👤 Authentication

Users can sign up and login.

📚 Courses

Users can view available language courses.

📖 Lessons

Each course contains lessons.

❓ Quiz

Users can answer quiz questions to test their knowledge.

🧠 Flashcards

Quick practice questions.

🔥 Streak System

Users maintain a learning streak by completing quizzes.

Example:

Day 1 → Quiz completed → streak = 1
Day 2 → Quiz completed → streak = 2
🧑‍💻 Deployment

Frontend deployed on:

Netlify / Vercel

Backend deployed on:

Render

Database:

Supabase
